stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_init: r = 0
    q_init --> q_check16: test upper 16 bits
    q_check16 --> q_shift16: !(x & 0xFFFF0000)
    q_check16 --> q_check8: x & 0xFFFF0000
    q_shift16 --> q_check8: r += 16, x <<= 16
    q_check8 --> q_shift8: !(x & 0xFF000000)
    q_check8 --> q_check4: x & 0xFF000000
    q_shift8 --> q_check4: r += 8, x <<= 8
    q_check4 --> q_shift4: !(x & 0xF0000000)
    q_check4 --> q_check2: x & 0xF0000000
    q_shift4 --> q_check2: r += 4, x <<= 4
    q_check2 --> q_shift2: !(x & 0xC0000000)
    q_check2 --> q_check1: x & 0xC0000000
    q_shift2 --> q_check1: r += 2, x <<= 2
    q_check1 --> q_inc: !(x & 0x80000000)
    q_check1 --> q_return: x & 0x80000000
    q_inc --> q_return: r += 1
    q_return --> [*]: return r
